SUMMARY:Cubs Summer Camp
DESCRIPTION:Three days under canvas at Pioneer Camp — Friday afternoon arrival\, Sunday afternoon collection. The Pack will be running a mix of campcraft\, water activities and the all-time-favourite night hike.\nThe kit list for this camp is linked below\; consent forms come home four weeks ahead. Bursary support is available — speak to Akela in confidence if cost would otherwise stop your Cub joining us.\n
